//[Reference] 'Hey ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! How are things?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011400=やあ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！調子はどう？
//[Reference] 'Did you hear that there's some big exec on the island right now?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011500=今、島にお偉いさんが来てるのは知ってる？
//[Reference] 'I...may have convinced a big game company to send someone out to pitch an idea...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011600=僕…大手のゲーム会社を説得して、アイデアを売り込みたいから人を送って欲しいって持ち掛けたんだ。
//[Reference] 'Do...do you think you could go and speak to them for me?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011700=その…僕の代わりに話をしてきてくれないかな？
//[Reference] 'Why don't you?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011800=どうして？
//[Validate] Delete this comment if or when the translation is accurate.
//[Reference] 'He uh... Well, let's just say he's mentioned a restraining order...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10011900=えーと、その…なんというか、接近禁止命令を出されたと言うか…
//[Reference] 'I might have been a little bit too persistent with my last pitch...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012000=最後の一押しがちょっとしつこかったのかなあ…
//[Reference] 'He goes home at the end of the day! Please, just pitch him this...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012100=あの人、夜には帰っちゃうんだ！お願いだよ、これを売り込んできてくれないかな…
//[Reference] '...and I'm sure he'll love it this time! When he does, get him to sign this for me!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012200=…それに今回は絶対に気に入ってもらえると思うんだ！その時は、これにサインをもらってきてよ！
//[Reference] 'That should seal the deal nicely!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012300=そうすれば取引成立さ！
//[Reference] 'He's back, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012400=お偉いさんが戻ってきたよ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'You should hurry on over! I'd rather not have to try and convince them again...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012500=急いで行ってきて！また説得するのはコリゴリだよ…
//[Reference] 'Ah. You couldn't find him in time?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012600=え、間に合わなかったの？
//[Reference] 'Well...not to worry. I think I can convince them to send him back in a few days...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012700=いやまあ…心配ないよ。数日後にまた来てもらえるように説得はできると思うし。
//[Reference] 'But perhaps not too many times! Let's not get this island blacklisted!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012800=でも何回もは勘弁だよ！この島がブラックリスト入りしちゃう！
//[Reference] 'Did you pitch my game yet, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10012900=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;、僕のゲームは売り込んでくれた？
//[Reference] 'Hurry! There's not much time left!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013000=急いで！あまり時間がないよ！
//[Reference] 'So that's what he said?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013100=それであの人はそんなことを言ってたの？
//[Reference] 'I suppose it's a step up from my previous attempts!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013200=僕の時よりも進展あったみたいだね！
//[Reference] 'Thanks a lot, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013300=ありがとう、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I know this isn't much, but I hope it'll at least express some of my gratitude!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013400=これじゃ少ないけど、せめてもの感謝の気持ちだよ！
//[Reference] 'I'll let you know when I've put together a better plan of action!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013500=もっと良い企画ができたら知らせるね！
//[Reference] 'This is it ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! I think I have it!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013600=これだよ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！閃いた！
//[Reference] 'I know what to do to impress that executive.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013700=お偉いさんを振り向かせる方法を思いついたんだ。
//[Reference] 'Over the past few days I've invested mili-'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013800=ここ数日でうん百…
//[Reference] '-a lot of money into developing an ingenious new AR game!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10013900=…たくさんお金をかけて新しいARゲームを開発したんだ！
//[Reference] 'You know, augmented reality - bringing the game into the real world!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014000=ほら、拡張現実。ゲームを現実世界に実現するんだ！
//[Reference] 'And guess what, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, it's your lucky day; you get to try the alpha!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014100=そしてなんと！^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;はラッキーだよ。このゲームのアルファ版をプレイさせてあげる！
//[Reference] 'Now what you need to do is take these ^c:d03e37;two devices^c:pop; and go catch some monsters!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014200=遊び方はこの^c:d03e37;2つのデバイス^c:pop;を持ってモンスターをゲットしに行くだけだよ！
//[Reference] 'You'll find them in the world, hanging around on plants, or maybe even in the rivers!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014300=モンスターはあちこちにいるよ。草むらに隠れていたり、川の中にいたりね！
//[Reference] 'But remember - your normal ^c:d03e37;bug net^c:pop; isn't going to work on these - they're not really there!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014400=でも忘れちゃいけないのが、いつも使っている^c:d03e37;虫取り網^c:pop;じゃ捕まえられないってこと。だって本当は実在しないからね！
//[Reference] 'Same goes for the ^c:d03e37;fishing rod^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014500=^c:d03e37;釣り竿^c:pop;も同じだよ！
//[Reference] 'Come back when you've caught 'em all!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014600=全部捕まえたらまた来てね！
//[Reference] 'Hmm... It looks like you're still missing a few.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014700=うーん…まだちょっと足りないみたい。
//[Reference] 'I think there are still ^c:d03e37;{0-LQuest_FishCount}^c:pop; in the ^c:1486b0;water^c:pop; and ^c:d03e37;{1-LQuest_BugCount}^c:pop; on ^c:1486b0;land^c:pop;.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014800=多分、まだ^c:1486b0;水中^c:pop;に^c:d03e37;{0-LQuest_FishCount}^c:pop;体と^c:1486b0;地上^c:pop;に^c:d03e37;{1-LQuest_BugCount}^c:pop;体かな。
//[Reference] 'I can't really get good stats on performance unless you catch every single one!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10014900=全部捕まえてくれないと、十分なデータが揃わないよ。
//[Reference] 'Wow, that was faster than I expected!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015000=わあ、思ったより早かったね！
//[Reference] 'Have you done this before, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015100=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;、もしかして前にやったことある？
//[Reference] 'Looks like it playtested pretty well - no major bugs to speak of!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015200=テストプレイはいい感じみたいだね。目立ったバグはないよ！
//[Reference] 'Well... Except for that one strange glitch I suppose...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015300=まあ…ちょっと変な不具合はあるみたいだけど…
//[Reference] 'How did it feel to you?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015400=やってみてどうだった？
//[Reference] 'It was great!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015500=最高だよ！
//[Reference] 'Well... There are a few-'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015600=いやまあ…ちょっとは…
//[Reference] 'Fantastic! I'm happy to hear that! I'll get started on the pitch right away!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015700=それは良かった！安心したよ！すぐに売り込もう！
//[Reference] 'Here, take these as a thank you!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015800=はいこれ、お礼に受け取ってよ！
//[Reference] 'Just a sample of the merch we're planning - have to get a head start before things take off, you know?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10015900=企画してる製品のサンプルだよ。色々進める前に先手を打っておかなきゃね。
//[Reference] 'Now I just need to fly on over to show this stuff off to the people in charge!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016000=それじゃあ僕は担当の人にコレを見せに行ってくるよ！
//[Reference] 'This is going to be an exciting time, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! Really exciting!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016100=きっとすごいことになるよ、c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！本当にワクワクするよ！
//[Reference] 'Hi ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016200=やあ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'I have some exciting news!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016300=面白いニュースがあるよ！
//[Reference] 'I managed to get a preliminary contract to begin opening an arcade to showcase some games!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016400=事前契約を取り付けて、ゲームを展示するゲームセンターを開けることになったんだ！
//[Reference] 'There's just one small problem...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016500=でも1つだけちょっと問題があって…
//[Reference] 'Contractors around here aren't the most...reliable, as I'm sure you know!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016600=この辺の建築業者はどうにも…君も知っての通り信用できない！
//[Reference] 'You've helped me out of some pretty tight situations in the past. I can count on you right?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016700=君には今まで色々とキツイところを助けてもらっただろ。今度も頼めないかな？
//[Reference] 'Of course!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016800=もちろん！
//[Reference] 'Maybe another time.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10016900=また今度ね。
//[Reference] 'Yes! That's just what I wanted to hear!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017000=よかった！そう言ってくれると思ったよ！
//[Reference] 'This ^c:d03e37;sign^c:pop; needs to go front and centre so everyone knows what it is!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017100=どんな建物なのか一目で分かるように、この^c:d03e37;看板^c:pop;を正面のど真ん中に置いてほしいんだ！
//[Reference] 'The ^c:d03e37;game cabinets^c:pop; are probably the most important part of the setup.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017200=^c:d03e37;ゲームの筐体^c:pop;は準備する上で一番欠かせないものだね。
//[Reference] 'Make sure you don't forget them!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017300=絶対に忘れないでね！
//[Reference] 'Oh. Well do let me know if you change your mind.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017400=そっか。また気が変わったら教えてよ。
//[Reference] 'Brilliant, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;! This is perfect!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017500=最高だよ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！文句なしだよ！
//[Reference] 'I'll get the first of our new games installed immediately!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017600=早速、最初の新しいゲームをインストールするよ！
//[Reference] 'How about you head over and give it a try?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017700=君も行って遊んでみないかい？
//[Reference] 'I'll give you something pretty special if you can beat the initial high score!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017800=最初のハイスコアを更新出来たら、すごくいいものをあげるよ！
//[Reference] 'How's things going, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10017900=調子はどう、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;？
//[Reference] 'It looks like you're not quite done yet, but progress is encouraging!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018000=まだ終わってないみたいだけど、進み具合はいい感じだよ！
//[Reference] 'How's it going with beating the score on that ^c:d03e37;cabinet^c:pop;?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018100=あの^c:d03e37;筐体^c:pop;のスコアは更新できそう？
//[Reference] 'If you haven't given it a shot yet, just head over to the ^c:1486b0;arcade^c:pop; and you'll find it easily!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018200=まだやってないなら、^c:1486b0;ゲームセンター^c:pop;に行けばすぐ見つかるよ！
//[Reference] 'Oh, nice! That was quicker than I expected!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018300=へえ、すごい！思ったより早く達成できたね！
//[Reference] 'Don't worry though - I have even bigger things planned!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018400=大丈夫、まだ計画はこんなものじゃないから！
//[Reference] 'But we'll get to that soon enough...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018500=まあ、すぐに分かるさ…
//[Reference] 'We may have received the preliminary contract, but there's still some work to be done to formalise it.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018600=事前契約を取り付けたけど、正式契約まで作業が残ってるんだ。
//[Reference] 'I'm sure I'll be needing your help again soon enough!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018700=またすぐに力を貸してもらうかもしれないね！
//[Reference] 'Oh good, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, you arrived just in time!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018800=ああ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。いいところに来てくれた！
//[Reference] 'That executive is back and it seems like he's brought someone with him...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10018900=お偉いさんが村に来たのはいいけど、連れがいるようなんだ…
//[Reference] 'I think this might be the final challenge, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019000=これは最後の挑戦になると思うんだ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;！
//[Reference] 'We absolutely have to win this!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019100=絶対に勝つぞー！
//[Reference] 'Come with me!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019200=一緒に来て！
//[Reference] 'We absolutely have to win this!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019300=絶対に勝つぞー！
//[Reference] 'You won't believe this, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;, but they've decided to fully endorse my projects!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019400=聞いて驚くなよ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。僕のプロジェクトが全部承認してもらえたんだ！
//[Reference] 'Hm? Oh, ^c:1486b0;Damian^c:pop;. Yeah, he is a bit intense, isn't he?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019500=え？ああ、^c:1486b0;ダミアン^c:pop;ね。うん、ちょっとグイグイくるよね。
//[Reference] 'I suspect he got a bit worse when I moved away...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019600=僕がいなくなってから、さらにヤバくなったかも…
//[Reference] 'Maybe he'll calm down a bit now that someone beat him at his own game!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019700=自分のゲームで誰かに負ければ、少しは大人しくなるかもね！
//[Reference] 'I do admit I'm pretty interested in getting that game in our ^c:1486b0;arcade^c:pop; though...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019800=あいつのゲームをうちの^c:1486b0;ゲームセンター^c:pop;に入れるのも悪くないな、とは思ってるけどね…
//[Reference] 'I wonder if I can convince him to let us host it?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10019900=どうにかうちに置けないかな？
//[Reference] 'But anyway... That's for later! We had a nice chat over here while you were gone.'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020000=とりあえず…それは後でいいや！君がいない間に身のある会話ができたよ！
//[Reference] 'I'm really not sure how to thank you enough - I don't doubt that you had a huge hand in making this possible!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020100=どうお礼を言えばいいか…君のおかげで実現できたようなものだしね！
//[Reference] 'This isn't much, but you're also welcome to come by the ^c:1486b0;arcade^c:pop; any time!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020200=お礼の足しにならないかもだけど、^c:1486b0;ゲームセンター^c:pop;に来たらいつでも歓迎するよ！
//[Reference] 'I have a feeling we'll be seeing a lot more of a certain someone in future...'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020300=これからは誰かさんともっと顔を合わせそうな気がするよ…
//[Reference] 'Heya ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;. How's it going?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020400=やあ、^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;。元気かい？
//[Reference] 'Tomti was looking for me?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020500=トムティが僕を探してた？
//[Reference] 'Ah! That person I played online with the other day!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020600=あぁ！最近オンラインで遊んだ人だ！
//[Reference] 'He wants me over for a LAN party huh?'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020700=一緒にLANパーティしたいって？
//[Reference] 'Oh wow. Haven't been to one of those in a while... Good to know there's another gamer around here!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020800=へぇ、そっか。そういうのしばらくやってなかったし…この辺にもゲーマーがいるってのはいいね！
//[Reference] 'This is the best thing to happen since I got here!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10020900=ここに来てから一番嬉しいよ！
//[Reference] 'Just bought a new deluxe controller too, this will be a great excuse to put it to the test!'
staxel.village.dialogue.NerdPrimary.line:10021000=ちょうどデラックスコントローラーを買ったばかりなんだ。試すのに絶好の機会になりそうだね！
